des: "This excellent chocolaty crust is lower in fat than most. Cocoa powder and nonfat yogurt make it delicious without adding lots of excess calories."
ins:
Preheat oven to 350 degrees F (175 degrees C).
In a medium bowl, mix together graham cracker crumbs, cocoa powder, yogurt, and brown sugar. Press mixture firmly into a 9 inch pie pan.
Bake in preheated oven for 5 minutes.
